[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32mTVSetSpec:[0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32mAs a TV set owner [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32mI want to be able to turn the TV on and off [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32mSo I can watch TV when I want [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32mAnd save energy when I'm not watching TV [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32mFeature: TV power button[0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m  Scenario: User presses power button when TV is off[0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m    Given a TV set that is switched off [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m    When the power button is pressed [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m    Then the TV should switch on [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m  Scenario: User presses power button when TV is on[0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m    Given a TV set that is switched on [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m    When the power button is pressed [0m[0m
[0m[[0minfo[0m] [0m[32m    Then the TV should switch off [0m[0m
